  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1279270/extras/a11067bf9c0a1bed528ae5c31fed59cd.avif?t=1748511689\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1279270/extras/564e50f0313c9b92ff937d4eeae70c6b.poster.avif?t=1748511689\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1279270/extras/564e50f0313c9b92ff937d4eeae70c6b.webm?t=1748511689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1279270/extras/420ecc2a9cb803caaa1fecc5442d95d8.avif?t=1748511689\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A legend has been passed down for generations... <br>When the world is in peril, seven heroes will come together and save the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Rolan, the uniting force that brings together these heroes of legend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic RPG Experience </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a Unique Fantasy World </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based Combat </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open-ended Exploration </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Endings</p></li></ul>",
